text:
@EddyCh  
Great picks! 🤝 You’ve clearly done your homework on the equipment layer. Choosing $ONTO and $VIAV is a high-conviction move: one dominates metrology for advanced packaging, while the other is the foundational testing layer for the 1.6T era. As a fellow holder, I completely agree—without precise testing, advanced capacity means nothing in 2026. 

Also, your shout-out to $BW (Babcock &amp; Wilcox) is a masterstroke! Its pivot into powering AI data centers via the Applied Digital partnership has turned it into a &quot;Hidden AI Infrastructure&quot; gem. Energy is indeed the final bottleneck of this cycle, and our views are perfectly aligned.

$VIAV - &quot;its extended and prob needs to rest... its +155% ytd...&quot;

and then it crushes earnings and is up another +26% premkt...

incredible how strong some of these co&#39;s are
